Spring Boot & Spring Cloud: Config Server, Eureka, Gateway, OpenFeign, Circuit Breaker (Resilience4j), Sleuth, Zipkin, etc.

Microservice Design: DDD, Bounded Contexts, Event-Driven Architecture, CQRS, and Saga patterns.

Persistence & Messaging: JPA, Redis, Kafka, RabbitMQ, PostgreSQL, MongoDB.

Security: Spring Security, OAuth2, JWT, Keycloak integration.

CI/CD & DevOps: Docker, Kubernetes, Helm, GitHub Actions, Jenkins, ArgoCD.

Observability: Prometheus, Grafana, ELK stack, distributed tracing, log correlation.

Testing & Quality: Unit, Integration, Contract (Pact), Testcontainers, WireMock.

Cloud-native deployment: AWS, GCP, Azure, Terraform, service discovery, load balancing.